ctor who bought him a state-of-the-art racing wheelchair.\", \"from\": 408, \"to\": 591, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ourPrivacy notice\", \"from\": 413, \"to\": 430}, {\"ngram\": \"Paralympicsthanks\", \"from\": 496, \"to\": 513}, {\"ngram\": \"a mystery benefactor\", \"from\": 517, \"to\": 537}, {\"ngram\": \"the-art\", \"from\": 564, \"to\": 571}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's fair to say Weir, a six-time Paralympic champion, has cut a disillusioned figure at recent Games.\", \"from\": 593, \"to\": 695, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Weir\", \"from\": 610, \"to\": 614}, {\"ngram\": \"a six-time Paralympic champion\", \"from\": 616, \"to\": 646}, {\"ngram\": \"a disillusioned figure\", \"from\": 656, \"to\": 678}, {\"ngram\": \"recent Games\", \"from\": 682, \"to\": 694}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After his three golds in London, he was left raging in Rio, claiming a member of the team accused him of 'throwing a race' and vowing never compete for Britain again.\", \"from\": 697, \"to\": 863, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 722, \"end\": 728, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999995770004702, \"rank\": 4.1939026595089767e-07, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 752, \"end\": 755, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9450101231892852, \"rank\": 0.05818972248150314, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 849, \"end\": 856, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9699467439439051, \"rank\": 0.03098385716563636, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his three golds\", \"from\": 703, \"to\": 718}, {\"ngram\": \"a member\", \"from\": 766, \"to\": 774}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 786}, {\"ngram\": \"a race\", \"from\": 812, \"to\": 818}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Back five years later in Tokyo, he was well off the pace, insisting he'd never compete on the track again as he could not be competitive with Switzerland's Marcel Hug, because of a lack of investment in his racing chair.\", \"from\": 865, \"to\": 1085, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 890, \"end\": 895, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9596435418237429, \"rank\": 0.0420533154047474, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1007, \"end\": 1018, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"score\": 0.9997446969109669, \"rank\": 0.0002546868323905846, \"text\": \"Switzerland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\"}, {\"begin\": 1021, \"end\": 1031, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcel_Hug\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Marcel Hug\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcel_Hug\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcel_Hug\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the pace\", \"from\": 913, \"to\": 921}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 955, \"to\": 964}, {\"ngram\": \"a lack\", \"from\": 1044, \"to\": 1050}, {\"ngram\": \"investment\", \"from\": 1054, \"to\": 1064}, {\"ngram\": \"his racing chair\", \"from\": 1068, \"to\": 1084}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is always been a sense that Weir is fuelled by a raging sense of injustice, whether it's lack of recognition, lack of prize money or lack of respect.\", \"from\": 1087, \"to\": 1242, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a sense\", \"from\": 1108, \"to\": 1115}, {\"ngram\": \"Weir\", \"from\": 1121, \"to\": 1125}, {\"ngram\": \"a raging sense\", \"from\": 1140, \"to\": 1154}, {\"ngram\": \"injustice\", \"from\": 1158, \"to\": 1167}, {\"ngram\": \"lack\", \"from\": 1182, \"to\": 1186}, {\"ngram\": \"recognition\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1201}, {\"ngram\": \"lack\", \"from\": 1203, \"to\": 1207}, {\"ngram\": \"prize money\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1222}, {\"ngram\": \"lack\", \"from\": 1226, \"to\": 1230}, {\"ngram\": \"respect\", \"from\": 1234, \"to\": 1241}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He is one of those athletes that can not be media trained, now competing at his seventhParalympicshe's certainly earned the right to say what he likes.\", \"from\": 1244, \"to\": 1395, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those athletes\", \"from\": 1257, \"to\": 1271}, {\"ngram\": \"media\", \"from\": 1288, \"to\": 1293}, {\"ngram\": \"his seventhParalympicshe\", \"from\": 1320, \"to\": 1344}, {\"ngram\": \"the right\", \"from\": 1364, \"to\": 1373}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Weir, now 45, is in a more reflective mood as he looks towards three events in Paris, the 1500m, 5000m and marathon and perhaps that's because he feels finally on a level-playing field in a sport where the appliance of science can be critical.\", \"from\": 1397, \"to\": 1644, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1480, \"end\": 1485, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999980736902, \"rank\": 1.9264818464242867e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Weir\", \"from\": 1401, \"to\": 1405}, {\"ngram\": \"a more reflective mood\", \"from\": 1421, \"to\": 1443}, {\"ngram\": \"three events\", \"from\": 1464, \"to\": 1476}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1500m\", \"from\": 1487, \"to\": 1496}, {\"ngram\": \"5000m\", \"from\": 1498, \"to\": 1503}, {\"ngram\": \"marathon\", \"from\": 1508, \"to\": 1516}, {\"ngram\": \"a level-playing field\", \"from\": 1564, \"to\": 1585}, {\"ngram\": \"a sport\", \"from\": 1589, \"to\": 1596}, {\"ngram\": \"the appliance\", \"from\": 1603, \"to\": 1616}, {\"ngram\": \"science\", \"from\": 1620, \"to\": 1627}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hug worked with a consortium of engineering teams including the Formula One company Sauber to design a chair that made him unstoppable in Tokyo, winning four golds, sometimes by a margin so whooping you'd need a telescope to see the silver medallist.\", \"from\": 1646, \"to\": 1896, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1710, \"end\": 1721, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Formula_One\", \"score\": 0.9999998976109107, \"rank\": 1.0238890485701313e-07, \"text\": \"Formula One\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Formula_One\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Formula_One\"}, {\"begin\": 1730, \"end\": 1736, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sauber_Motorsport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.148721570751488e-19, \"text\": \"Sauber\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sauber_Motorsport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sauber_Motorsport\"}, {\"begin\": 1784, \"end\": 1789, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9596435418237429, \"rank\": 0.0420533154047474, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hug\", \"from\": 1646, \"to\": 1649}, {\"ngram\": \"a consortium\", \"from\": 1662, \"to\": 1674}, {\"ngram\": \"engineering teams\", \"from\": 1678, \"to\": 1695}, {\"ngram\": \"a chair\", \"from\": 1747, \"to\": 1754}, {\"ngram\": \"four golds\", \"from\": 1799, \"to\": 1809}, {\"ngram\": \"a margin\", \"from\": 1824, \"to\": 1832}, {\"ngram\": \"a telescope\", \"from\": 1856, \"to\": 1867}, {\"ngram\": \"the silver medallist\", \"from\": 1875, \"to\": 1895}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, an increasingly frustrated Weir was racing in ten-year old aluminium chair, while Hug flew in high-tech carbon fibre, benefitting from a power-to-weight ratio that gave him such an advantage the rest were racing for the minor medals.\", \"from\": 1898, \"to\": 2142, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an increasingly frustrated Weir\", \"from\": 1909, \"to\": 1940}, {\"ngram\": \"ten-year old aluminium chair\", \"from\": 1955, \"to\": 1983}, {\"ngram\": \"Hug\", \"from\": 1991, \"to\": 1994}, {\"ngram\": \"high-tech carbon fibre\", \"from\": 2003, \"to\": 2025}, {\"ngram\": \"weight\", \"from\": 2055, \"to\": 2061}, {\"ngram\": \"such an advantage\", \"from\": 2082, \"to\": 2099}, {\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 2100, \"to\": 2108}, {\"ngram\": \"the minor medals\", \"from\": 2125, \"to\": 2141}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Other countries have gone away from us,\\\" he moaned.\", \"from\": 2144, \"to\": 2196, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Other countries\", \"from\": 2145, \"to\": 2160}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2181, \"to\": 2183}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not all down to the chair but it helps a lot.\\\"\", \"from\": 2197, \"to\": 2249, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the chair\", \"from\": 2219, \"to\": 2228}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2242, \"to\": 2247}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, a call after last year's London Marathon - in which Weir finished nine minutes behind his rival - changed everything.\", \"from\": 2251, \"to\": 2377, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a call\", \"from\": 2260, \"to\": 2266}, {\"ngram\": \"last year's London Marathon\", \"from\": 2273, \"to\": 2300}, {\"ngram\": \"Weir\", \"from\": 2312, \"to\": 2316}, {\"ngram\": \"nine minutes\", \"from\": 2326, \"to\": 2338}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 2366, \"to\": 2376}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It really changed everything that one call and I could not be more grateful,\\\" said Weir, who is keeping the name of his supporter to himself.\", \"from\": 2379, \"to\": 2521, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 2398, \"to\": 2408}, {\"ngram\": \"Weir\", \"from\": 2463, \"to\": 2467}, {\"ngram\": \"the name\", \"from\": 2484, \"to\": 2492}, {\"ngram\": \"his supporter\", \"from\": 2496, \"to\": 2509}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's really helped me mentally, it's a joy to be in, it's a piece of machinery made especially for me, it's the best chair I have ever raced in.\", \"from\": 2523, \"to\": 2668, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a joy\", \"from\": 2561, \"to\": 2566}, {\"ngram\": \"a piece\", \"from\": 2582, \"to\": 2589}, {\"ngram\": \"machinery\", \"from\": 2593, \"to\": 2602}, {\"ngram\": \"the best chair\", \"from\": 2632, \"to\": 2646}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have enjoyed training so much in the last eight or nine months.\", \"from\": 2670, \"to\": 2736, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the last eight or nine months\", \"from\": 2706, \"to\": 2735}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Marcel wiped us all out in Tokyo because he had this chair that had been under wraps, now I feel like I am competitive.\", \"from\": 2737, \"to\": 2856, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2764, \"end\": 2769, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9596435418237429, \"rank\": 0.0420533154047474, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Marcel\", \"from\": 2737, \"to\": 2743}, {\"ngram\": \"us\"