m pretty proud of myself.\\\"\", \"from\": 3119, \"to\": 3272, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 3174, \"to\": 3183}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Weir and Hug's rivalry has dominated wheelchair racing for more than a decade but the two are surprisingly close, with the Brit a regular visitor to training camps in the Swiss Alps.\", \"from\": 3274, \"to\": 3456, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3445, \"end\": 3455, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swiss_Alps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Swiss Alps\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swiss_Alps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swiss_Alps\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Weir\", \"from\": 3274, \"to\": 3278}, {\"ngram\": \"Hug's rivalry\", \"from\": 3283, \"to\": 3296}, {\"ngram\": \"wheelchair racing\", \"from\": 3311, \"to\": 3328}, {\"ngram\": \"more than a decade\", \"from\": 3333, \"to\": 3351}, {\"ngram\": \"the Brit\", \"from\": 3393, \"to\": 3401}, {\"ngram\": \"training camps\", \"from\": 3423, \"to\": 3437}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are great friends, I can not say a bad word about him.\", \"from\": 3458, \"to\": 3516, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"great friends\", \"from\": 3466, \"to\": 3479}, {\"ngram\": \"a bad word\", \"from\": 3495, \"to\": 3505}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have trained a lot with him this year and we enjoy doing camps together,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 3517, \"to\": 3602, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 3532, \"to\": 3537}, {\"ngram\": \"camps\", \"from\": 3576, \"to\": 3581}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Him and his team have always been very open and they want the sport to do well.\", \"from\": 3604, \"to\": 3684, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his team\", \"from\": 3613, \"to\": 3621}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 3663, \"to\": 3672}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have been one of his biggest rivals for years but he's got a lot of respect for me and I have for him.\", \"from\": 3685, \"to\": 3789, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his biggest rivals\", \"from\": 3704, \"to\": 3722}, {\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 3727, \"to\": 3732}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 3746, \"to\": 3751}, {\"ngram\": \"respect\", \"from\": 3755, \"to\": 3762}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have both pushed each other but he's going to be hard to beat, he's a phenomenal athlete.\\\"\", \"from\": 3790, \"to\": 3883, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a phenomenal athlete\", \"from\": 3861, \"to\": 3881}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Aldi are proud Official Partners of Team GB & ParalympicsGB, supporting all athletes through toParis 2024 Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 3885, \"to\": 4222, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3885, \"end\": 3889, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aldi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Aldi\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aldi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aldi\"}, {\"begin\": 4043, \"end\": 4054, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.019564290525978e-18, \"text\": \"Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"proud Official Partners\", \"from\": 3894, \"to\": 3917}, {\"ngram\": \"Team GB\", \"from\": 3921, \"to\": 3928}, {\"ngram\": \"ParalympicsGB\", \"from\": 3931, \"to\": 3944}, {\"ngram\": \"all athletes\", \"from\": 3957, \"to\": 3969}, {\"ngram\": \"toParis 2024 Join thought-provoking conversations\", \"from\": 3978, \"t